Stage 5 of 8: Money and Craft

Open a bank account early; auction bids and some purchases are backed
by bank liens, and your balance is shared across every branch.

Learn the player-driven economy: shops, the remote market, and the
live auction channel. When you want a break from fighting, professions
like fishing, mining, and smithing earn steadily and feed the market.

